zmix = 2, # lake mixing depth in m
Pin = NA, # P inflow concentration in mg P m^-3

QP1 = NA, # algae cell P quota in mg P mg^-1 C^-1

QN1 = NA # algae cell N quota in mg N mg^-1 C^-1
